h1. logging 

h2. Purpose

The @logging@ plug-in sets up Grails' support for [Logging|guide:logging] with "Log4j":http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2/index.html.

h2. Examples

Example log statements:

{code}
log.info "Configuration data source"

try {
	..
}
catch(Exception e) {
	log.error "Error: ${e.message}", e
}
{code}

h2. Description

Refer to the section on [Logging|guide:logging] in the Grails user guide which details how Grails' logging support.




